    <h1 class="heading1">Plastic Surgery Department at Aatura Hospital</h1>
    <h4 class="heading4">At Aatura Hospital, our Plastic Surgery Department is dedicated to providing aesthetic and reconstructive surgical procedures to enhance appearance, restore function, and improve quality of life. Led by board-certified plastic surgeons and supported by a team of skilled healthcare professionals, we offer a wide range of plastic surgery services tailored to meet the unique needs and goals of each patient.</h4>

    <div class="content1">
        <div class="content-left">
            <h3>Our Services</h3>
            <h4>Cosmetic Procedures</h4>
            <p>We offer a variety of cosmetic surgical procedures to enhance facial and body features, improve symmetry, and achieve desired aesthetic outcomes. These may include facelifts, rhinoplasty, breast augmentation, liposuction, abdominoplasty, and body contouring procedures.</p>

            <h4>Reconstructive Surgery</h4>
            <p>We specialize in reconstructive surgical procedures to restore form and function to areas of the body affected by congenital anomalies, trauma, cancer, or previous surgeries. Our plastic surgeons perform reconstructive surgeries such as breast reconstruction, skin grafting, flap reconstruction, microsurgery, and scar revision.</p>

            <h4>Breast Surgery</h4>
            <p>We offer a comprehensive range of breast surgery procedures to address various concerns related to breast appearance, size, shape, and symmetry. These may include breast augmentation, breast lift, breast reduction, breast reconstruction following mastectomy, and correction of breast asymmetry.</p>

            <h4>Facial Rejuvenation</h4>
            <p>We provide facial rejuvenation procedures to reverse signs of aging, restore youthful contours, and enhance facial harmony. Our plastic surgeons perform procedures such as facelifts, brow lifts, eyelid surgery (blepharoplasty), neck lifts, and fat transfer to rejuvenate the face and achieve natural-looking results.</p>

            <h4>Body Contouring</h4>
            <p>We offer body contouring procedures to improve body shape, remove excess fat and skin, and enhance body contours. These may include liposuction, abdominoplasty (tummy tuck), thigh lift, arm lift, buttock augmentation, and post-bariatric surgery body contouring.</p>

            <h4>Minimally Invasive Procedures</h4>
            <p>In addition to traditional surgical techniques, we offer minimally invasive procedures such as injectable treatments (Botox, dermal fillers), laser therapy, chemical peels, and non-surgical skin tightening procedures to achieve subtle improvements in appearance with minimal downtime.</p>
        </div>
